  § F1-CORRECTNESS PROOF STACK (3-way composable)
    source.cssl
      → lex+parse+HIR+AD-legality+refinement-obligations+MIR+AD-walker+SMT
      → apply_fwd : real tangent-carrying arith ops .per primitive chain-rule
      → apply_bwd : reverse-iter adjoint-accumulation + cssl.diff.bwd_return
      → ad_gate::run_killer_app_gate :
          11 canonical cases (FAdd/FSub/FMul/FDiv/FNeg + sqrt/sin/cos/exp/log + chain)
          AnalyticExpr algebra .w/ simplify + evaluate + to_smt + to_term
          MirAdjointInterpreter reconstructs AnalyticExpr per adjoint-out
          verify_gradient_case : symbolic-simplify + 11-point sampling
      → 3 verification paths :
          (a) structural-simplify (AnalyticExpr::simplify)
          (b) sampling-numeric   (equivalent_by_sampling 11-point deterministic)
          (c) SMT-unsat-verdict  (run_smt_verification[_via_query] ↔ Z3/CVC5)
      → 2 attestation layers :
          (d) SignedKillerAppGateReport : BLAKE3 + Ed25519 .over canonical-payload
              AttestationVerdict { format_matches, payload_hash_matches,
                                   signature_verifies, gate_is_green }
